data.description: You will love this gorgeous home located in the 9th Street neighborhood.  Close to local schools and businesses and just minutes away from the Colorado River.  This home has 4 bedrooms, 2 baths plus a bonus room with it's own A/C.  There is a 2 car garage and large driveway. The spacious back yard has a pebble and concrete patio, a great patio covering and includes a 24' x 16' above ground pool! More pictures to come soon! Property is being sold in it's current condition. Buyer & buyer's agent to verify accuracy of all information.
